          <profiles>
            <profile name="Lion Helm" typeId="57617267656172204974656d23232344415441232323" typeName="Wargear" hidden="false" id="d606-9113-7e3e-9ff0">
              <characteristics>
                <characteristic name="Description" typeId="4465736372697074696f6e23232344415441232323">The Lion Helm provides Azrael, and all models in any unit he joins, with a 4+ Invulnerable Save.

The Lion Helm is carried by the Helmet Bearer, which is represented on the tabletop by a separate miniature that will always remain as close as possible to Azrael, without getting in the way of other miniatures. The helmet bearer takes no part in the game and is ignored or moved out of the way for purposes of determining lines of sight, charging, etc. If Azrael is killed, the Helmet Bearer is also removed.</characteristic>
              </characteristics>
            </profile>
          </profiles>
        </selectionEntry>
